  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487840/extras/caa831b3d84815db372a57a1daacc7f4.poster.avif?t=1610465334\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487840/extras/caa831b3d84815db372a57a1daacc7f4.webm?t=1610465334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487840/extras/caa831b3d84815db372a57a1daacc7f4.mp4?t=1610465334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Chess Destroyer is like a normal chess game but bigger and some new rules:<br>the map gets bigger every turn<br>more enemies come<br>you can capture an enemy unit by killing it with your pawn unit,<br>or acquire new ones by completing simple quests appearing in the bottom left corner of the screen<br><br>Kill enemy units, find friendly ones, defend the king, and survive as long as you can!<br><br>Lore: To escape from death the king had to run from the battleground. with his 2 pawns, he jumped from his chess board onto another smaller one. but it's growing and enemies are coming.<br><br>The rest is up to you. good luck!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487840/extras/caa831b3d84815db372a57a1daacc7f4.poster.avif?t=1610465334\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487840/extras/caa831b3d84815db372a57a1daacc7f4.webm?t=1610465334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487840/extras/caa831b3d84815db372a57a1daacc7f4.mp4?t=1610465334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Chess Destroyer is like a normal chess game but bigger and some new rules:<br>the map gets bigger every turn<br>more enemies come<br>you can capture an enemy unit by killing it with your pawn unit,<br>or acquire new ones by completing simple quests appearing in the bottom left corner of the screen<br><br>Kill enemy units, find friendly ones, defend the king, and survive as long as you can!<br><br>Lore: To escape from death the king had to run from the battleground. with his 2 pawns, he jumped from his chess board onto another smaller one. but it's growing and enemies are coming.<br><br>The rest is up to you. good luck!",
